{"tid":2045042,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【國安法壓港】或延 BNO 留英期限　藍韜文：不會對港視而不見　不會背棄對港責任","createTime":"2020-05-31T13:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T08:03:39.000Z","uid":357334,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"47744562d01c324da0f080faa87d37236c9c0f1c","tid":2045042,"uid":357334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T13:47:33.000Z","msg":"全國人大通過「港區國安法」的決定草案，引發國際社會關注。英國外相藍韜文（Dominic Raab）日前表示，若中國不停止訂立國安法，將會更改 BNO 在英國的居留條件，居留期由 6 個月變成 12 個月，又指是為將來取得公民權鋪路。藍韜文今日接受《BBC》訪問時表示，英國不會視而不見，亦不會背棄對香港的責任，重申早前提出延長 BNO 簽證的建議，是回應中國即將在香港實施國家安全法。<br />\n<br />\n藍韜文指，如果中國落實港區安全法，便會給予持有 BNO 護照的人來英國的權利，並估計部份人會前往英國（a fraction of them would actually come）。他強調，英國不會對香港視而不見，亦不會背棄英國對香港人的責任。<br />\n<br />\n新聞來源：<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E5%A3%93%E6%B8%AF-%E6%88%96%E5%BB%B6-bno-%E7%95%99%E8%8B%B1%E6%9C%9F%E9%99%90-%E8%97%8D%E9%9F%9C%E6%96%87-%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E5%B0%8D%E6%B8%AF%E8%A6%96%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%8B-%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E8%83%8C%E6%A3%84%E5%B0%8D%E6%B8%AF%E8%B2%AC%E4%BB%BB/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25A3%2593%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E6%2588%2596%25E5%25BB%25B6-bno-%25E7%2595%2599%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%259C%259F%25E9%2599%2590-%25E8%2597%258D%25E9%259F%259C%25E6%2596%2587-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25A6%2596%25E8%2580%258C%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25A6%258B-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%2583%258C%25E6%25A3%2584%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E4%25BB%25BB%2F&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGseYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=99466132\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25A3%2593%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E6%2588%2596%25E5%25BB%25B6-bno-%25E7%2595%2599%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%259C%259F%25E9%2599%2590-%25E8%2597%258D%25E9%259F%259C%25E6%2596%2587